This project's base code came from a template written by Flamewing.
Source link: https://medium.com/@flamewing1314/typing-speed-test-game-in-html-css-javascript-827e50dbcdbd

Code was then modified to include two instead of just one typing tests.
The second test uses remapped keys.
The website also introduces background information about this project
and has a post activity survey linked for users to share input. 

All modifications were made by Sophie Biltz.